---
title: Apricot-Glazed Halloumi & Mumbai Veggie Toss with Cucumber Raita & Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful halloumi coated in apricot sauce meets roasted vegetables tossed with Mumbai-style spices, and there’s a tangy yoghurt dressing to finish it off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
